A group, Indomitable Tinubu Support Organisation, has stated that the National Leader of the All Progressives Congress, Asiwaju Bola Tinubu, is experienced to fix Nigeria’s challenges. The group made this known in a statement by its Director-General, Abdoulbaq Balogun, on Sunday. The statement read, “Asiwaju’s indelible mark in the continuous transformation of Lagos State where he drew the Lagos state development master plan, which can be replicated at the federal level, is a testimony to his preparedness to lead the country to prosperity and help solve its challenges. He is a master strategist with grit, courage, and resourceful. “We also commend Nigerians both home and abroad, who believe in Asiwaju Tinubu and mobilised resources to get the nomination form for the leading presidential hopeful. We express confidence in the capacity of the National Leader of All Progressives Congress, Asiwaju Tinubu, to address the challenges facing the country. “We urge Nigerians to go out and support the aspiration of a man who understands the complexity of Nigeria and one who can harness all the resources to make the country great and realise its potential because the man fit for the job is no other person than Asiwaju Bola Tinubu.” Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com